  "title": "Electrical Design Engineer - Entry Welcome, Tuas, Transport Provided",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare material requisition lists for job requirements.</li><li>Plan and design electrical switchboards, consoles and control panels according to customer's requirements and Terasaki standards.</li><li>Prepare approval drawings, shop drawings, final drawings / documents, short circuit calculations, instruction manuals as required for submission to clients and shop floor production.</li><li>Co-ordinate with clients and consultants on the technical requirements. Attend technical discussions with clients and consultants when required.</li><li>Feedback to Sales & Marketing Department on the changes of technical requirements by clients for claims of additional costs and time.</li><li>Check and follow-up on design and shop drawings with production departments.</li><li>Develop and improve on design of electrical switchboards, consoles and control panels. While taking note of quality, standard, cost effective designs are to be considered.</li><li>Assist and advise Sales & Marketing Department on technical matters, provide technical backup for securing of contracts.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Electrical Engineering </li><li>With or without working experience</li><li>Knowledge of AutoCAD & SolidWorks</li></ul><p><br /><strong>_________________________________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on <strong>“Quick Apply”</strong></p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</p><p>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</p><p>3) Expected salary</p><p>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Joni</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R1106641</strong></p>",
